A dramatic cyberpunk scene of the Strait of Malacca at night, viewed from above like a tactical display. Sleek black speedboats with harsh neon-blue engine trails cut through dark waters between massive illuminated cargo ships. In the distance, the glowing skyline of Singapore rises with towering holographic data streams connecting buildings. The water reflects crimson and electric blue lights. Radar circles and scanning grids overlay the scene like a high-tech surveillance system. The atmosphere is tense and cinematic, with storm clouds gathering overhead lit by distant lightning. The cargo vessels appear vulnerable, their containers stacked high, while the small predatory boats circle like sharks. Rain begins to fall, creating streaks through the neon reflections on the black water.
